= Hope (Ar-Rajā’)

#sc[Definition:] It means expectation, desire, hope, and awaiting something
beloved.

== Categories of Hope:
=== 1. Hope as Worship:

This is hoping in Allāh alone with no partner. It is of two types:

- Praiseworthy Hope: This is hope combined with action and obedience to Allāh.

- Blameworthy Hope: This is hope without any action — it is mere wishful
  thinking and deception.

=== 2. Hope which is Shirk:

Hoping in someone other than Allāh for something that only Allāh has power over.

=== 3. Natural Hope:

Hoping for something from someone who possesses it and has the ability to
fulfill it, like saying: “I hope you attend.”

